Then you're dead.

00:50:13.720 --> 00:50:14.439
PROFESSOR: No.

00:50:14.439 --> 00:50:15.730
You want to maximize show offs.

00:50:15.730 --> 00:50:17.090
So if we have the
entertainment thing,

00:50:17.090 --> 00:50:18.210
then that would be maximized.

00:50:18.210 --> 00:50:19.290
And then you'd have minus.

00:50:19.290 --> 00:50:20.136
AUDIENCE: Then you'd
