00:51:02.890 --> 00:51:03.515
PROFESSOR: Yep.

00:51:06.180 --> 00:51:09.690
So I'm going to have a note
0, with all possible foot

00:51:09.690 --> 00:51:11.760
positions.

00:51:11.760 --> 00:51:15.540
And then this is going to
be connected to a source,

00:51:15.540 --> 00:51:18.087
by edges of weight 0.

00:51:18.087 --> 00:51:20.670
So the intuition is that I get
to choose my starting position,

00:51:20.670 --> 00:51:21.710
right?

00:51:21.710 --> 00:51:23.360
Starting position.

