I see the first note.

00:51:24.440 --> 00:51:26.020
I make a move.

00:51:26.020 --> 00:51:28.280
So I want to be able to
choose the starting position.

00:51:28.280 --> 00:51:29.820
That's why I have
all those notes.

00:51:29.820 --> 00:51:32.370
And then make a move to
touch the first note.

00:51:35.842 --> 00:51:38.322
AUDIENCE: The starting
